channel.title: DiverseScape - UNLEASHED! Looking for players, staff, GFX Makers + Webby Makers!
channel.description:
[b][i][size=24pt][center]DiverseScape UNLEASHED!
[font=arial black][color=red]Hello, all! Owner Mike from DiverseScape! We are currently looking for Players, Staff, GFX Makers, Website, and webclient makers. We are currently undergoing webclient problems, and we need help. We are a brand new server that is amazing. We have many things that other servers don't have to offer! Current website: [url=http://www.DiverseScape2.webs.com/]http://www.DiverseScape2.webs.com/[/url] We hope you join! We have many updates coming and are looking for suggestions. Major drop party to get the economy going at 10-15 players. Hope to see all of you in DiverseScape!
[font=arial][center][size=24pt] PICTURES:[/size][IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2q1cc51.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2ml06p.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/thyw.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/acr1tw.png[/img][/center]
